<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinics-ai-tools-help-predict-severe-asthma-risks-in-young-children/">Mayo Clinic&amp;#8217;s AI tools help predict severe asthma risks in young children&nbsp;</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
